title: International Factball: Colombia v Ivory Coast
content: The QI Elves in association with www.visitengland.com bring you the eighth episode of this No Such Thing As A Fish Factball special - the only football podcast that has absolutely nothing to do with football. Today Dan Schreiber (@schreiberland), James Harkin (@jamesharkin), Andrew Hunter Murray (@andrewhunterm) and Anna Ptaszynski (@nosuchthing) pit Colombia against the Ivory Coast to find out which is the most Quite Interesting country.
